abstract: Ligaya Mishan reviews Tone-Cafe, Georgian restaurant near Gramercy Park in Manhattan.
lead_paragraph: Food comes quickly, on paper plates or encased in plastic tubs, originally destined for takeout. Nevertheless, it is a feast.

headline.main: Toné-Café Brings Georgian Cuisine to Gramercy Park
headline.print_headline: Takeout Georgian Food Worth Staying For
